author: Dillon Essma
text: The play for me is the under. It’s Jose in a big game. If they score, they will kill it off. And tbh Inter do the same under Inzaghi against top teams. Inter’s D is also great, and still have struggled to blow top teams doors off. I would say Inter 1-0 or maybe 1-1 draw. #SerieA

author: Dillon Essma
text: Big test for Roma today. Unbeaten in last 9 #SerieA matches. I think they’ve played some bad teams in this stretch and good teams on bad form. They’ve also dropped points to what I would call mediocre teams. Inter title on the line and the clear best in 🇮🇹. Not totally buying it.
